{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "CloudChemistryFixedpH",
        "description": "Aqueous-phase S(IV) to S(VI) oxidation chemistry in cloud droplets with pH supplied as an external input. Migrated from Aerosol.jl@c8c640bb src/cloud_chemistry.jl:269. Assembles water autoionization, SO2/H2O2/O3 Henry law equilibria, and all S(IV) oxidation pathways (O3, H2O2, Fe/Mn-catalyzed) from Seinfeld & Pandis (2006) Chapter 7. Flat (no ESM subsystem references) to satisfy depends_on: none. CO2/NH3/HNO3 equilibria outputs are not connected to CloudChemistryFixedpH own variables in the upstream MTK component, so they are omitted; p_CO2/p_NH3/p_HNO3 remain as declared parameters.",
        "tags": ["aerosol", "aqueous_equilibria", "cloud_chemistry", "sulfate_formation", "seinfeld-pandis-ch7"],
        "created": "2026-05-21T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": ["Aerosol.jl contributors", "EarthSciModels migration (esm-l5r)"],
        "references": [{"citation": "Seinfeld, J. H., & Pandis, S. N. (2006). Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics: From Air Pollution to Climate Change, 2nd ed. Wiley. Chapter 7: water autoionization (Sec 7.3.1, Eqs 7.10-7.13, Table 7.4), SO2 equilibria (Sec 7.3.3, Eqs 7.30-7.45), H2O2 equilibria (Sec 7.3.6), O3 dissolution, S(IV) oxidation kinetics (Sec 7.5, Eqs 7.79-7.80, 7.84, 7.92, 7.101, 7.102), rate conversions (Sec 7.4, Eqs 7.75-7.78)."}]
    },
    "models": {
        "CloudChemistryFixedpH": {
            "reference": {
                "notes": "source_ref: Aerosol.jl@c8c640bb:src/cloud_chemistry.jl:269\n\nUpstream CloudChemistryFixedpH is an MTK @component that assembles eight subsystems: WaterEquilibrium, CO2Equilibria, SO2Equilibria, NH3Equilibria, HNO3Equilibria, H2O2Equilibria, O3Equilibria, SulfateFormation. pH is an external input; H_plus = C_ref * 10^(-pH_input).\n\nFlat migration rationale: the tracker marks depends_on: none. H2O2Equilibria has no standalone ESM on main; its physics is inlined directly. CO2/NH3/HNO3 equilibria outputs are not connected back to CloudChemistryFixedpH own @variables in the upstream source (only SO2/H2O2/O3/water subsystem outputs are aliased). p_CO2, p_NH3, p_HNO3 remain as parameters matching upstream @variables.\n\nThe flattened system has 26 state variables and 26 algebraic equations, fully explicit and triangular:\n  1. H_plus = C_ref * 10^(-pH_input)\n  2-3. K_w (van Hoff, S&P Eq. 7.10), OH_minus = K_w/H_plus (Eq. 7.11)\n  4-9. H_SO2, K_s1, K_s2, SO2_aq, HSO3_minus, SO3_2minus (SO2 equilibria, Eqs. 7.33-7.35)\n  10. S_IV_total = SO2_aq + HSO3_minus + SO3_2minus (Eq. 7.39)\n  11-12. H_H2O2 (van Hoff), H2O2_aq = H_H2O2 * p_H2O2\n  13-14. H_O3 (van Hoff), O3_aq = H_O3 * p_O3\n  15. R_O3 = (k_O3_0*SO2_aq + k_O3_1*HSO3_minus + k_O3_2*SO3_2minus)*O3_aq (Eq. 7.79)\n  16. R_H2O2 = k_H2O2*H_plus*H2O2_aq*HSO3_minus/(1 + K_H2O2_eq*H_plus) (Eq. 7.84)\n  17-20. R_Mn_term, R_Fe_term, R_synergy_term, R_FeMn (Eq. 7.102)\n  21-23. R_total, S_VI_production, w_L\n  24-26. R_ppb_hr (Eq. 7.75), R_percent_hr (Eq. 7.76), tau_SO2 (Eq. 7.78)\n\nRate constants (SulfateFormation @constants, M to SI: divide by 1000 for mol/m^3):\n  k_O3_0=24, k_O3_1=370, k_O3_2=1.5e6 m^3/(mol*s); k_H2O2=75 m^6/(mol^2*s), K_H2O2_eq=0.013 m^3/mol\n  k_Mn=0.75, k_Fe=2.6 m^3/(mol*s); k_FeMn=1e4 m^6/(mol^2*s)\n\nHenry constants at 298 K (M/atm / 101325 * 1000 = mol/m^3/Pa):\n  H_SO2_298=0.012138, H_H2O2_298=987.17, H_O3_298=1.086e-4 mol/m^3/Pa\n\nDissociation constants at 298 K (M * 1000 = mol/m^3):\n  K_s1_298=13, K_s2_298=6.6e-5, K_w_298=1e-8 mol^2/m^6\n\nR_gas=8.314 J/(mol*K) for van Hoff equilibrium corrections.\nR_gas_conv=8.31446 J/(mol*K) for Section 7.4 rate conversions (matches SulfateFormation @constants).\n\nDefaults: pH=4.0, T=298.15 K, p_SO2=5.07e-4 Pa (~5 ppb), p_H2O2=5.07e-5 Pa (~0.5 ppb), p_O3=4.053e-3 Pa (~40 ppb), Fe_III=Mn_II=1e-3 mol/m^3, L=0.5 g/m^3, xi_SO2=5e-9."
            },
            "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-06},
            "variables": {
                "C_ref":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3",     "default": 1000.0,      "description": "Reference concentration (1 mol/L = 1000 mol/m3) for pH to H_plus conversion. Upstream @constants."},
                "R_gas":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol/K",     "default": 8.314,       "description": "Gas constant for van Hoff equilibrium-constant and Henry law temperature corrections. Upstream WaterEquilibrium/SO2Equilibria @constants 8.314 J/(mol*K)."},
                "R_gas_conv":  {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol/K",     "default": 8.31446,     "description": "Gas constant for Section 7.4 rate-conversion equations. Upstream SulfateFormation @constants 8.31446 J/(mol*K)."},
                "T_ref":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "K",           "default": 298.0,       "description": "Reference temperature for van Hoff corrections. Upstream @constants 298.0 K."},
                "K_w_298":     {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol^2/m^6",   "default": 1e-08,       "description": "Water autoionization constant at 298 K. 1.0e-14 M^2 * 1e6 = 1e-8 mol^2/m^6 (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "dH_Kw":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol",       "default": 55856.4,     "description": "Enthalpy of water autoionization. 13.35 kcal/mol * 4184 = 55856.4 J/mol (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "H_SO2_298":   {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3/Pa",  "default": 0.012138,    "description": "Henry law constant for SO2 at 298 K. 1.23 M/atm / 101325 * 1000 = 0.012138 mol/m^3/Pa (S&P Sec 7.3.3)."},
                "dH_H_SO2":    {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol",       "default": -26150.0,    "description": "Enthalpy of SO2 dissolution. -6.25 kcal/mol * 4184 = -26150 J/mol (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "K_s1_298":    {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3",     "default": 13.0,        "description": "First SO2 dissociation constant at 298 K (SO2.H2O <-> H+ + HSO3-). 1.3e-2 M * 1000 = 13 mol/m^3 (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "K_s2_298":    {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3",     "default": 6.6e-05,     "description": "Second SO2 dissociation constant at 298 K (HSO3- <-> H+ + SO3^2-). 6.6e-8 M * 1000 = 6.6e-5 mol/m^3 (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "dH_Ks1":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol",       "default": -17405.44,   "description": "Enthalpy for first SO2 dissociation. -4.16 kcal/mol * 4184 = -17405.44 J/mol (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "dH_Ks2":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol",       "default": -9330.32,    "description": "Enthalpy for second SO2 dissociation. -2.23 kcal/mol * 4184 = -9330.32 J/mol (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "H_H2O2_298":  {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3/Pa",  "default": 987.17,      "description": "Henry law constant for H2O2 at 298 K. 1.0e5 M/atm / 101325 * 1000 = 987.17 mol/m^3/Pa (S&P Sec 7.3.6)."},
                "dH_H_H2O2":   {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol",       "default": -60668.0,    "description": "Enthalpy of H2O2 dissolution. -14.5 kcal/mol * 4184 = -60668 J/mol (S&P Table 7.4)."},
                "H_O3_298":    {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3/Pa",  "default": 0.0001086,   "description": "Henry law constant for O3 at 298 K. 1.1e-2 M/atm / 101325 * 1000 = 1.086e-4 mol/m^3/Pa."},
                "dH_H_O3":     {"type": "parameter", "units": "J/mol",       "default": -21087.36,   "description": "Enthalpy of O3 dissolution. -5.04 kcal/mol * 4184 = -21087.36 J/mol."},
                "k_O3_0":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/mol/s",   "default": 24.0,        "description": "O3 oxidation rate constant for SO2.H2O channel (k0). 2.4e4 M^-1s^-1 / 1000 = 24 m^3/(mol*s) (S&P Eq. 7.79)."},
                "k_O3_1":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/mol/s",   "default": 370.0,       "description": "O3 oxidation rate constant for HSO3- channel (k1). 3.7e5 M^-1s^-1 / 1000 = 370 m^3/(mol*s) (S&P Eq. 7.79)."},
                "k_O3_2":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/mol/s",   "default": 1500000.0,   "description": "O3 oxidation rate constant for SO3^2- channel (k2). 1.5e9 M^-1s^-1 / 1000 = 1.5e6 m^3/(mol*s) (S&P Eq. 7.79)."},
                "k_H2O2":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^6/mol^2/s", "default": 75.0,        "description": "H2O2 oxidation rate constant (k). 7.5e7 M^-2s^-1 / 1e6 = 75 m^6/(mol^2*s) (S&P Eq. 7.84)."},
                "K_H2O2_eq":   {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/mol",     "default": 0.013,       "description": "H2O2 oxidation denominator constant (K). 13 M^-1 / 1000 = 0.013 m^3/mol (S&P Eq. 7.84)."},
                "k_Mn":        {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/mol/s",   "default": 0.75,        "description": "Mn-only rate constant in Fe/Mn synergism. 750 M^-1s^-1 / 1000 = 0.75 m^3/(mol*s) (S&P Eq. 7.102)."},
                "k_Fe":        {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/mol/s",   "default": 2.6,         "description": "Fe-only rate constant in Fe/Mn synergism. 2600 M^-1s^-1 / 1000 = 2.6 m^3/(mol*s) (S&P Eq. 7.102)."},
                "k_FeMn":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^6/mol^2/s", "default": 10000.0,     "description": "Fe/Mn synergistic rate constant. 1.0e10 M^-2s^-1 / 1e6 = 1e4 m^6/(mol^2*s) (S&P Eq. 7.102)."},
                "p_total":     {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 101325.0,    "description": "Total atmospheric pressure for rate-conversion equations (Eqs. 7.75-7.78)."},
                "rho_w_inv":   {"type": "parameter", "units": "m^3/g",       "default": 1e-06,       "description": "Inverse liquid water density for LWC conversion: 1/(1e6 g/m^3) = 1e-6 m^3/g."},
                "s_per_hr":    {"type": "parameter", "units": "s",           "default": 3600.0,      "description": "Seconds per hour for rate-conversion equations."},
                "ppb_factor":  {"type": "parameter", "units": "1",           "default": 1e9,         "description": "Parts-per-billion scaling factor (1e9) for Eq. 7.75."},
                "pct_factor":  {"type": "parameter", "units": "1",           "default": 100.0,       "description": "Percent scaling factor for Eq. 7.76."},
                "T":           {"type": "parameter", "units": "K",           "default": 298.15,      "description": "Temperature. Drives all van Hoff equilibrium-constant and Henry law corrections."},
                "pH_input":    {"type": "parameter", "units": "1",           "default": 4.0,         "description": "Input pH (dimensionless). H_plus = C_ref * 10^(-pH_input). Default 4.0 is representative of moderately acidic cloud droplets."},
                "p_SO2":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 5.07e-04,    "description": "Partial pressure of SO2 (~5 ppb at 1 atm). Drives SO2 Henry law dissolution."},
                "p_H2O2":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 5.07e-05,    "description": "Partial pressure of H2O2 (~0.5 ppb at 1 atm). Drives H2O2 Henry law dissolution."},
                "p_O3":        {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 0.004053,    "description": "Partial pressure of O3 (~40 ppb at 1 atm). Drives O3 Henry law dissolution."},
                "p_CO2":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 40.0,        "description": "Partial pressure of CO2 (~400 ppm). Declared to match upstream @variables; CO2 equilibria outputs not connected in CloudChemistryFixedpH and are omitted from this flat migration."},
                "p_NH3":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 1.52e-04,    "description": "Partial pressure of NH3 (~1.5 ppb). Declared to match upstream @variables; NH3 equilibria outputs not connected and are omitted."},
                "p_HNO3":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "Pa",          "default": 1.52e-05,    "description": "Partial pressure of HNO3 (~0.15 ppb). Declared to match upstream @variables; HNO3 equilibria outputs not connected and are omitted."},
                "Fe_III":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3",     "default": 0.001,       "description": "Fe(III) concentration in cloud droplet. Metal catalyst for S(IV) oxidation."},
                "Mn_II":       {"type": "parameter", "units": "mol/m^3",     "default": 0.001,       "description": "Mn(II) concentration in cloud droplet. Metal catalyst for S(IV) oxidation."},
                "L":           {"type": "parameter", "units": "g/m^3",       "default": 0.5,         "description": "Liquid water content. Used in rate-conversion equations (Eqs. 7.75-7.78)."},
                "xi_SO2":      {"type": "parameter", "units": "1",           "default": 5e-09,       "description": "SO2 gas-phase mixing ratio (dimensionless, ~5 ppb). Used in S(IV) lifetime and percent-conversion rate equations (Eqs. 7.76, 7.78)."},
                "H_plus":      {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Hydrogen ion concentration derived from pH_input. H_plus = C_ref * 10^(-pH_input)."},
                "K_w":         {"type": "state", "units": "mol^2/m^6",  "description": "Water autoionization constant at T (van Hoff, S&P Eq. 7.10)."},
                "OH_minus":    {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Hydroxide concentration = K_w / H_plus (S&P Eq. 7.11)."},
                "H_SO2":       {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/Pa", "description": "Henry law constant for SO2 at T (van Hoff)."},
                "K_s1":        {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "First SO2 dissociation constant at T (van Hoff, S&P Eq. 7.34)."},
                "K_s2":        {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Second SO2 dissociation constant at T (van Hoff, S&P Eq. 7.35)."},
                "SO2_aq":      {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Aqueous SO2 [SO2.H2O] = H_SO2 * p_SO2 (S&P Eq. 7.33)."},
                "HSO3_minus":  {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Bisulfite [HSO3-] = K_s1 * SO2_aq / H_plus (S&P Eq. 7.34)."},
                "SO3_2minus":  {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Sulfite [SO3^2-] = K_s2 * HSO3_minus / H_plus (S&P Eq. 7.35)."},
                "S_IV_total":  {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Total S(IV) = SO2_aq + HSO3_minus + SO3_2minus (S&P Eq. 7.39)."},
                "H_H2O2":      {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/Pa", "description": "Henry law constant for H2O2 at T (van Hoff)."},
                "H2O2_aq":     {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Aqueous H2O2 = H_H2O2 * p_H2O2."},
                "H_O3":        {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/Pa", "description": "Henry law constant for O3 at T (van Hoff)."},
                "O3_aq":       {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3",    "description": "Aqueous O3 = H_O3 * p_O3."},
                "R_O3":        {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s",  "description": "S(IV) oxidation rate by O3: (k0*[SO2.H2O] + k1*[HSO3-] + k2*[SO3^2-])*[O3(aq)] (S&P Eq. 7.79)."},
                "R_H2O2":      {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s",  "description": "S(IV) oxidation rate by H2O2: k*[H+]*[H2O2]*[HSO3-]/(1+K*[H+]) (S&P Eq. 7.84)."},
                "R_Mn_term":   {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s",  "description": "Mn-only contribution: k_Mn * [Mn] * [S(IV)] (S&P Eq. 7.102 first term)."},
                "R_Fe_term":   {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s",  "description": "Fe-only contribution: k_Fe * [Fe] * [S(IV)] (S&P Eq. 7.102 second term)."},
                "R_synergy_term": {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s", "description": "Synergistic contribution: k_FeMn * [Mn] * [Fe] * [S(IV)] (S&P Eq. 7.102 third term)."},
                "R_FeMn":      {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s",  "description": "Total Fe/Mn synergistic oxidation: R_Mn_term + R_Fe_term + R_synergy_term (S&P Eq. 7.102)."},
                "R_total":     {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s",  "description": "Total S(IV) oxidation rate: R_O3 + R_H2O2 + R_FeMn."},
                "S_VI_production": {"type": "state", "units": "mol/m^3/s", "description": "Sulfate production rate = R_total (stoichiometric 1:1)."},
                "w_L":         {"type": "state", "units": "1",           "description": "Liquid water volume ratio: w_L = rho_w_inv * L (S&P Sec 7.4)."},
                "R_ppb_hr":    {"type": "state", "units": "1",           "description": "S(IV) oxidation rate in ppb/hr: 1e9*3600*w_L*R_gas_conv*T*R_total/p_total (S&P Eq. 7.75)."},
                "R_percent_hr": {"type": "state", "units": "1",          "description": "S(IV) as %/hr: 100*3600*R_total*w_L*R_gas_conv*T/(p_total*xi_SO2) (S&P Eq. 7.76)."},
                "tau_SO2":     {"type": "state", "units": "s",           "description": "SO2 lifetime: xi_SO2*p_total/(w_L*R_gas_conv*T*R_total) (S&P Eq. 7.78)."}
            },
            "equations": [
                {"lhs": "H_plus", "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["C_ref", {"op": "^", "args": [10, {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "pH_input"]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "K_w",    "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["K_w_298", {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [-1, "dH_Kw"]}, "R_gas"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [1, "T"]}, {"op": "/", "args": [-1, "T_ref"]}]}]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "OH_minus",   "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": ["K_w", "H_plus"]}},
                {"lhs": "H_SO2",  "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["H_SO2_298",  {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": ["dH_H_SO2",  "R_gas"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [1, "T_ref"]}, {"op": "/", "args": [-1, "T"]}]}]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "K_s1",   "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["K_s1_298",   {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [-1, "dH_Ks1"]},  "R_gas"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [1, "T"]}, {"op": "/", "args": [-1, "T_ref"]}]}]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "K_s2",   "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["K_s2_298",   {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [-1, "dH_Ks2"]},  "R_gas"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [1, "T"]}, {"op": "/", "args": [-1, "T_ref"]}]}]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "SO2_aq",     "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["H_SO2", "p_SO2"]}},
                {"lhs": "HSO3_minus", "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["K_s1", "SO2_aq"]}, "H_plus"]}},
                {"lhs": "SO3_2minus", "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["K_s2", "HSO3_minus"]}, "H_plus"]}},
                {"lhs": "S_IV_total", "rhs": {"op": "+", "args": ["SO2_aq", "HSO3_minus", "SO3_2minus"]}},
                {"lhs": "H_H2O2", "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["H_H2O2_298", {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": ["dH_H_H2O2", "R_gas"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [1, "T_ref"]}, {"op": "/", "args": [-1, "T"]}]}]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "H2O2_aq",    "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["H_H2O2", "p_H2O2"]}},
                {"lhs": "H_O3",   "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["H_O3_298",   {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": ["dH_H_O3",   "R_gas"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "/", "args": [1, "T_ref"]}, {"op": "/", "args": [-1, "T"]}]}]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "O3_aq",  "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["H_O3", "p_O3"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_O3",   "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": [{"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["k_O3_0", "SO2_aq"]}, {"op": "*", "args": ["k_O3_1", "HSO3_minus"]}, {"op": "*", "args": ["k_O3_2", "SO3_2minus"]}]}, "O3_aq"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_H2O2", "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["k_H2O2", "H_plus", "H2O2_aq", "HSO3_minus"]}, {"op": "+", "args": [1, {"op": "*", "args": ["K_H2O2_eq", "H_plus"]}]}]}},
                {"lhs": "R_Mn_term",      "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["k_Mn",  "Mn_II",  "S_IV_total"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_Fe_term",      "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["k_Fe",  "Fe_III", "S_IV_total"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_synergy_term", "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["k_FeMn", "Mn_II", "Fe_III", "S_IV_total"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_FeMn",         "rhs": {"op": "+", "args": ["R_Mn_term", "R_Fe_term", "R_synergy_term"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_total",        "rhs": {"op": "+", "args": ["R_O3", "R_H2O2", "R_FeMn"]}},
                {"lhs": "S_VI_production","rhs": "R_total"},
                {"lhs": "w_L",            "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["rho_w_inv", "L"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_ppb_hr",       "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["ppb_factor", "s_per_hr", "w_L", "R_gas_conv", "T", "R_total"]}, "p_total"]}},
                {"lhs": "R_percent_hr",   "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["pct_factor", "s_per_hr", "R_total", "w_L", "R_gas_conv", "T"]}, {"op": "*", "args": ["p_total", "xi_SO2"]}]}},
                {"lhs": "tau_SO2",        "rhs": {"op": "/", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": ["xi_SO2", "p_total"]}, {"op": "*", "args": ["w_L", "R_gas_conv", "T", "R_total"]}]}}
            ],
            "tests": [
                {
                    "id": "default_parameters",
                    "description": "Default cloud conditions: pH 4.0, T=298.15 K, p_SO2=5.07e-4 Pa (~5 ppb), p_H2O2=5.07e-5 Pa (~0.5 ppb), p_O3=4.053e-3 Pa (~40 ppb), Fe_III=Mn_II=1e-3 mol/m3, L=0.5 g/m3, xi_SO2=5e-9. Pins all 26 state variables at t=0.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "H_plus",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0e-1},
                        {"variable": "K_w",            "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0114069199e-08},
                        {"variable": "OH_minus",       "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0114069199e-07},
                        {"variable": "H_SO2",          "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.2073716957e-02},
                        {"variable": "K_s1",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.2954133958e+01},
                        {"variable": "K_s2",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 6.5875072145e-05},
                        {"variable": "SO2_aq",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 6.1213744972e-06},
                        {"variable": "HSO3_minus",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 7.9297105246e-04},
                        {"variable": "SO3_2minus",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 5.2237025289e-07},
                        {"variable": "S_IV_total",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 7.9961479721e-04},
                        {"variable": "H_H2O2",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 9.7508325363e+02},
                        {"variable": "H2O2_aq",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 4.9436720959e-02},
                        {"variable": "H_O3",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0813596291e-04},
                        {"variable": "O3_aq",          "time": 0.0, "expected": 4.3827505768e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_O3",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 4.7206675786e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_H2O2",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.9363244269e-04},
                        {"variable": "R_Mn_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 5.9971109791e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_Fe_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.0789984727e-06},
                        {"variable": "R_synergy_term", "time": 0.0, "expected": 7.9961479721e-06},
                        {"variable": "R_FeMn",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0674857543e-05},
                        {"variable": "R_total",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 3.0477936699e-04},
                        {"variable": "S_VI_production","time": 0.0, "expected": 3.0477936699e-04},
                        {"variable": "w_L",            "time": 0.0, "expected": 5.0e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_ppb_hr",       "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.3421786227e+01},
                        {"variable": "R_percent_hr",   "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.6843572455e+02},
                        {"variable": "tau_SO2",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.3411031658e+03}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "cold_cloud",
                    "description": "T=283.15 K (10 deg C). Henry constants increase: H_H2O2 ~3.6x, H_SO2 ~1.75x. Tests van Hoff temperature sensitivity of all equilibria.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"T": 283.15},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "H_plus",   "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0e-1},
                        {"variable": "K_w",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 3.0654872712e-09},
                        {"variable": "OH_minus", "time": 0.0, "expected": 3.0654872712e-08},
                        {"variable": "H_SO2",    "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.1113001615e-02},
                        {"variable": "H_H2O2",   "time": 0.0, "expected": 3.5655502019e+03},
                        {"variable": "H2O2_aq",  "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.8077339524e-01},
                        {"variable": "H_O3",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.6970345401e-04},
                        {"variable": "O3_aq",    "time": 0.0, "expected": 6.8780809911e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_H2O2",   "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.7236104397e-03},
                        {"variable": "R_total",  "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.7528088763e-03},
                        {"variable": "R_ppb_hr", "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.1512842594e+02},
                        {"variable": "tau_SO2",  "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.5634713888e+02}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "higher_pH",
                    "description": "pH=5.0 (H_plus=0.01 mol/m3). HSO3_minus 10x larger, SO3_2minus 100x larger vs pH 4, enhancing R_O3 (large k2 for SO3^2-).",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"pH_input": 5.0},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "H_plus",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0e-02},
                        {"variable": "OH_minus",   "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0114069199e-06},
                        {"variable": "HSO3_minus", "time": 0.0, "expected": 7.9297105246e-03},
                        {"variable": "SO3_2minus", "time": 0.0, "expected": 5.2237025289e-05},
                        {"variable": "S_IV_total", "time": 0.0, "expected": 7.9880689244e-03},
                        {"variable": "R_O3",       "time": 0.0, "expected": 3.5627238201e-05},
                        {"variable": "R_H2O2",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.9397594800e-04},
                        {"variable": "R_total",    "time": 0.0, "expected": 4.3624390634e-04},
                        {"variable": "tau_SO2",    "time": 0.0, "expected": 9.3695423135e+02}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "o3_pathway_isolation",
                    "description": "O3 pathway only: p_H2O2=0, Fe_III=Mn_II=0. R_H2O2, R_FeMn and metal terms must be exactly zero; R_total = R_O3.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"p_H2O2": 0.0, "Fe_III": 0.0, "Mn_II": 0.0},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "H2O2_aq",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0},
                        {"variable": "R_O3",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 4.7206675786e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_H2O2",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_Mn_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_Fe_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_synergy_term", "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_FeMn",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_total",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 4.7206675786e-07}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "h2o2_pathway_isolation",
                    "description": "H2O2 pathway only: p_O3=0, Fe_III=Mn_II=0. R_O3, R_FeMn must be zero; R_total = R_H2O2.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"p_O3": 0.0, "Fe_III": 0.0, "Mn_II": 0.0},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "O3_aq",          "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0},
                        {"variable": "R_O3",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_H2O2",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.9363244269e-04},
                        {"variable": "R_Mn_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_Fe_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_synergy_term", "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_FeMn",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_total",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.9363244269e-04}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "femn_pathway_isolation",
                    "description": "Fe/Mn pathway only: p_O3=0, p_H2O2=0. R_O3 and R_H2O2 must be zero; R_total = R_FeMn = R_Mn_term + R_Fe_term + R_synergy_term.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"p_O3": 0.0, "p_H2O2": 0.0},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "O3_aq",          "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0},
                        {"variable": "H2O2_aq",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0},
                        {"variable": "R_O3",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_H2O2",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 0.0, "tolerance": {"rel": 1e-6, "abs": 1e-30}},
                        {"variable": "R_Mn_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 5.9971109791e-07},
                        {"variable": "R_Fe_term",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.0789984727e-06},
                        {"variable": "R_synergy_term", "time": 0.0, "expected": 7.9961479721e-06},
                        {"variable": "R_FeMn",         "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0674857543e-05},
                        {"variable": "R_total",        "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0674857543e-05}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "rate_conversion_double_L",
                    "description": "Doubling L to 1.0 g/m3 doubles w_L, R_ppb_hr, R_percent_hr and halves tau_SO2. Verifies Section 7.4 rate-conversion scaling (Eqs. 7.75-7.78).",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"L": 1.0},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "w_L",           "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.0e-06},
                        {"variable": "R_ppb_hr",      "time": 0.0, "expected": 2.6843572455e+01},
                        {"variable": "R_percent_hr",  "time": 0.0, "expected": 5.3687144909e+02},
                        {"variable": "tau_SO2",       "time": 0.0, "expected": 6.7055158290e+02}
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "examples": [
                {
                    "id": "ph_sweep_oxidation_rates",
                    "description": "S(IV) oxidation rates vs pH from 2 to 7. Shows pH-independence of R_H2O2 (dominant at all pH) and strong pH-enhancement of R_O3 (SO3^2- channel with k2=1.5e6 m^3/(mol*s)).",
                    "initial_state": {"type": "per_variable", "values": {}},
                    "parameters": {},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "parameter_sweep": {"type": "cartesian", "dimensions": [{"parameter": "pH_input", "range": {"start": 2.0, "stop": 7.0, "count": 20, "scale": "linear"}}]},
                    "plots": [
                        {"id": "R_total_vs_pH", "type": "line", "description": "Total S(IV) oxidation rate vs pH.", "x": {"variable": "pH_input", "label": "pH"}, "y": {"variable": "R_total", "label": "R_total (mol/m3/s)"}},
                        {"id": "R_O3_vs_pH",    "type": "line", "description": "O3 pathway rate vs pH.", "x": {"variable": "pH_input", "label": "pH"}, "y": {"variable": "R_O3",    "label": "R_O3 (mol/m3/s)"}},
                        {"id": "R_H2O2_vs_pH",  "type": "line", "description": "H2O2 pathway rate vs pH.", "x": {"variable": "pH_input", "label": "pH"}, "y": {"variable": "R_H2O2",  "label": "R_H2O2 (mol/m3/s)"}}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "temperature_sensitivity",
                    "description": "Rate and equilibrium sensitivity to T (270-310 K). Cold clouds enhance Henry law dissolution of H2O2 and SO2, increasing aqueous concentrations and accelerating S(IV) oxidation.",
                    "initial_state": {"type": "per_variable", "values": {}},
                    "parameters": {},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "parameter_sweep": {"type": "cartesian", "dimensions": [{"parameter": "T", "range": {"start": 270.0, "stop": 310.0, "count": 15, "scale": "linear"}}]},
                    "plots": [
                        {"id": "tau_SO2_vs_T",  "type": "line", "description": "SO2 lifetime vs temperature.", "x": {"variable": "T", "label": "Temperature (K)"}, "y": {"variable": "tau_SO2", "label": "tau_SO2 (s)"}},
                        {"id": "H_H2O2_vs_T",   "type": "line", "description": "H2O2 Henry law constant vs temperature.", "x": {"variable": "T", "label": "Temperature (K)"}, "y": {"variable": "H_H2O2", "label": "H_H2O2 (mol/m3/Pa)"}}
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    }
}
